<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6369509">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6369509/" class="title-link">战争，便是死神那恐怖的车轮</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6369509"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/philodraco/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2582305-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/philodraco/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">聖寶劍橡葉騎士</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-02"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-02 00:29:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6369509_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  对于我们大多数人而言，“战争”两个字是一个遥远却模糊不清的概念，时而还会带有若干浪漫的色彩。加上影视剧，尤其是这些年的影视剧不遗余力地推波助澜，“战争”二字头上更是被带上了神话般的光环。这使得不少人们对于这两个字非但没有恐惧、厌恶之心，相反却心向往之，结果...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6369509/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6369509_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6369509_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7118439">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7118439/" class="title-link">这才是战争</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7118439"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/51817685/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51817685-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51817685/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">嬴政的崛起</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-10-04"
      class="main-meta">2014-10-04 09:05:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7118439_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  战争的残酷远远不是我们这些和平时期坐在家里看着大片的人们所能想象得到的，如果你曾对战争充满憧憬和期待，不妨去回顾几遍《拯救大兵瑞恩》、《兄弟连》、《血战太平洋》。如果这些还不够刺激到你，那么就来读一读斯文·哈塞尔的这一系列小说吧。 这是我读过有史以来最震撼的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
